title: Marc Chagall Boxed Note Cards
description:
Send your best wishes with the beautifully reproduced artwork on these full-color full-size Notecard Boxes, packaged in a large format two piece glossy reusable box. Marc Chagall's expressive and dreamlike paintings are reproduced in full color as notecards, including five images for a sophisticated stationery set.

Set includes 4 cards of each of the following 5 images:
The Glowing Bouquet, 1972
The Creation of Man, 1956-58
The Window, 1927-28
Mother and Child, 1948-53
Songs of Songs IV, 1958
  • Dimensions: 5.5 x 7.5 x 1.5 in.
  • Materials: Large-format glossy 2-piece box. Cards printed on coated paper stock
  • 20 notecards and envelopes, 4 each of 5 images
